# NavBar

`TxNavBar` renders a compact application header with a centered title, optional safe-area spacer, left and right action zones, and a default back button.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/nav-bar/src/types.ts`, `TxNavBar.vue`, and `nav-bar.test.ts`.

## Basic Usage

::::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="NavBarNavBarDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  function noop() {}
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxNavBar title="Settings" show-back @back="noop" @click-right="noop">
      <template #right>
        <span>Save</span>
      </template>
    </TxNavBar>
  </template>
